    <!-- Service Start -->
    <div class="container services-section">
        <div class="services-header text-center">
            <p class="section-title">Recyclabe Materials</p>
            <h1>Accepted Scraps</h1>
        </div>
        <div id="serviceCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                            <div class="card service-card">
                                <div class="service-image">
                                    <img src="../img/plastic.png" alt="Book Appointment">
                                </div>
                                <div class="service-content">
                                    <h5>Plastic</h5>
                                    <p>It refers to discarded plastic materials that can be recycled and repurposed into new products, reducing environmental pollution and conserving resources. The recycling process involves collection, sorting, cleaning, shredding, melting, and remanufacturing, which helps save energy and provides economic benefits.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                            <div class="card service-card">
                                <div class="service-image">
                                    <img src="../img/yero.jpg" alt="GPS Location">
                                </div>
                                <div class="service-content">
                                    <h5>Yero</h5>
                                    <p>It is discarded or damaged metal sheets commonly used in roofing and construction, collected for recycling. These sheets are sorted, cleaned, and processed to create new metal products, reducing the need for raw materials and conserving energy. Recycling scrap corrugated iron helps minimize environmental impact.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                            <div class="card service-card">
                                <div class="service-image">
                                    <img src="../img/cardboard.png" alt="Badge">
                                </div>
                                <div class="service-content">
                                    <h5>Card Board</h5>
                                    <p>It is used or discarded cardboard materials, such as boxes and collected for recycling. These materials are sorted, cleaned, and processed into new cardboard products, helping to reduce landfill waste and save natural resources. Recycling scrap cardboard supports sustainable waste management.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                            <div class="card service-card">
                                <div class="service-image">
                                    <img src="../img/paper.png" alt="Profile">
                                </div>
                                <div class="service-content">
                                    <h5>Paper</h5>
                                    <p>It is discarded or used paper products like newspapers, office paper, and magazines, collected for recycling. These materials are sorted, cleaned, and processed to produce new paper products, reducing the need for virgin pulp. Recycling scrap paper helps conserve natural resources, save energy, and minimize landfill waste.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                            <div class="card service-card">
                                <div class="service-image">
                                    <img src="../img/steel.jpg" alt="Notification">
                                </div>
                                <div class="service-content">
                                    <h5>Steel</h5>
                                    <p>It consists of discarded or obsolete steel items, such as old appliances, cars, and construction materials, collected for recycling. This steel is sorted, cleaned, and melted down to create new steel products, reducing the need for raw materials and conserving energy. Recycling scrap steel supports decreases environmental pollution.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                            <div class="card service-card">
                                <div class="service-image">
                                    <img src="../img/copper.jpeg" alt="Home">
                                </div>
                                <div class="service-content">
                                    <h5>Copper</h5>
                                    <p>It is consists of discarded or unused copper materials, such as wiring, pipes, and electrical components, collected for recycling. The copper is sorted, cleaned, and processed to produce new copper products, reducing the need for mining and conserving energy. Recycling scrap copper helps efficient resource management.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#serviceCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
